--- documentation, pipeline:maruku
Description
-----------

This CLI plugin displays information about plugins.

It searches for a plugin matching the given argument or shows all
plugins if no argument is given. If the search returns exactly one
plugin, information about this plugin is displayed, including:

* author
* summary
* dependencies
* plugin parameters
* plugin documentation (only in extended mode)

Otherwise a list of matching plugins is displayed sothat the search can
be further narrowed down.